charges.charge_description: 18:641.F PUBLIC MONEY, PROPERTY OR RECORDS (Theft of Government Property) (1s-8s)

charges.charge_disposition: 12 months imprisonment on each of Counts 1s, 2s, 3s, 4s, 5s, 6s, 7s, 8s to be served concurrently; 2 years supervised release on each of Counts 1s, 2s, 3s, 4s, 5s, 6s, 7s, 8s, to be served concurrently; $800.00 special assessment ($100.00 on each of Counts 1s through 8s); $16,352.63 restitution. (1s-8s)

charges.charge_description: 18:641.F PUBLIC MONEY, PROPERTY OR RECORDS-Theft of government property (1-3)

Steal and/or convert money and/or other property belonging to the United States, falsely represent a particular social security number was his, when in fact it was not, in violation of 18 USC 641 and 42 USC 408(a)(7)(B) [5:98-m-581]
